  <!-- ## Description & History -->

  <description>
    Hello! We are Bearly Humans, and we are currently developing our first game, Squirrelville!
  </description>

  <history>
    Bearly Humans was formed from a group of Australian university students from various backgrounds for their final year project. After an initial period of pitching various projects, Squirrelville was chosen as their project to develop fully. Unfortunately due to the COVID-19 outbreak in Melbourne, their initial plans to exhibit at PAX Aus were upended, and Bearly Humans had to adapt to fully developing their first large-scale project while also in the midst of a lockdown.
  </history>

